title: Ep 41 | Miss Kay's Fantasy Football Team, Willie's Growing Family, and Phil’s Disaster Interview
description:
Miss Kay and Willie join the show today and talk about Miss Kay’s fantasy football team. Willie gives a rundown of all the new family members he has gained over the last year, and they all remember the time Kathie Lee asked Phil if he has dogs.
